Package: colortable
Type: Package
Title: Style Your Table Elements
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Ellis Hughes
Maintainer: Ellis Hughes <ellishughes@live.com>
Description: Provide access to the "color_vctr" object that allows for coloring
    of the elements of your vectors. The styling will appear when you print to 
    console, and also apply to the printing in knited tables.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Imports: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    cli,
    vctrs
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
URL: https://github.com/thebioengineer/colortable
BugReports: https://github.com/thebioengineer/colortable/issues
VignetteBuilder: knitr
